snippet.title: If 2020 Was A Person | Ashish Chanchlani | Kunal Chhabhria | Akash Dodeja | Simran Dhanwani
snippet.description:
You can download upGrad from the link below:
http://bit.ly/DownloadUpGrad

Iss baar bhi sab sach likhunga, Ye video ka idea @ashish chanchlani vines  ne diya... usse ek concept sochne bola aur usne 5..6 bheje.. but 2020 wala baad mein bana nahi sakte kyunki comments aaenge... abhi kyu daal rahe ho...2021 chal raha hai... iss liye humne ye bana diya... jis joke pe hassi aaegi woh Ashish ne likha hai aur jispe nahi aaegi woh maine...aur baaki ka @Jashan Sirwani  ne..


Cast: ACV Rozgaar Yojna ke harr sadasya ko kaam mila ismein
@Akash Dodeja @Simran Dhanwani @Rohit Sadhwani @Jashan Sirwani @Tanish Sirwani aur sabka seth @Anmol Sachar apne Andheri ke PentHouse mein chill kar rahe the...

Shoot toh humne color camera se kiya... Christopher Kedare ka dost.. Sid Kedare ne shoot kiya. 

Editing: Titanic Movie ke poster ke printout 5 rupaye mein bechne wala Tanish Sirwani ne edit kiya star ka... Uske baad thoda maine kiya aur Ashish ne music and sound effects lagaye 15 min mein..

Thumbnail: Jaane do...main nahi bataunga ki Grishim Nawani ne cutout kiya aur hum baaki mazdooro ne milke baaki ka thumbnail design kiya.

Upload karne mein late ho raha hai... 2 baje bola tha, 2:13 ho rahe hai.. iss liye description yaha khatam karte hai, baaki video dekh ke dosto ko zarur bhejna...

Fcuk U 2020

Happy New Year

#AshishChanchlani #KunalChhabhria #Acvians #FU2020

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3070 - Kaun Banegi Vijeta Jodi | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता का उल्टा चश्मा
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu)

snippet.title: 01 Jan | Daily Current Affairs Live Show #435 | India & World | Hindi & English | Kumar Gaurav Sir |
snippet.description:
#Currentaffairs #KumarGauravSir #UtkarshClasses

01 Jan | Daily Current Affairs Live Show #435 | India & World | Hindi & English | Kumar Gaurav Sir |

प्रिय विद्यार्थियों,
प्रत्येक प्रतियोगी परीक्षाओं के लिए दैनिक समसामयिकी (करंट अफेयर्स) की महत्वपूर्ण भूमिका रहती है। इसी को ध्यान में रखकर आपकी तैयारी को और अधिक मजबूती प्रदान करने के लिए  प्रतिदिन प्रातः 6:00  बजे आपके प्यारे कुमार गौरव सर आप से रूबरू होते हैं और चर्चा करते हैं सुर्खियों में बने उन मुद्दों पर, जो कि परीक्षा के दृष्टिकोण को ध्यान में रखकर आपके लिए लेकर आते है। उनके इसी समर्पण भाव को आप सभी ने असीम स्नेह दिया और यह शो भारत का नंबर वन लाइव करंट अफेयर्स शो बन गया। इस नियमित लाइव क्लासेस में आप प्रमुख प्रतियोगी परीक्षाओं के लिए राष्ट्रीय एवं अंतर्राष्ट्रीय समसामयिकी जैसे- खेल, अंतर्राष्ट्रीय संबंध, विज्ञान व तकनीकी, राजव्यवस्था, पर्यावरण इत्यादि से जुड़ी कई जानकारियाँ प्राप्त करते हैं।

इस लाइव सेशन के बेहतरीन फीचर्स इस प्रकार है :
●दैनिक सुर्खियाँ ( #Daily_Current_Affairs )
●प्रेरक वाक्य या Motivational Quote  
●MCQ यानि बहुविकल्पात्मक प्रश्नों के माध्यम से करंट अफेयर्स की तैयारी
●10 सबसे महत्वपूर्ण प्रश्न 
●फूलपत्ती वाला सवाल 
● गुरुमंत्र
●Today's GS Questions
● विज्ञप्तियों से संबंधित जानकारियाँ इत्यादि।

तो जानिए बीते दिन के करंट अफेयर्स Kumar Gaurav Sir के साथ प्रतिदिन सुबह 6:00 बजे ।

http://bit.ly/38A6nU9
▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬
DAILY CURRENT AFFAIRS SHOWS :-

snippet.localized.title: 01 Jan | Daily Current Affairs Live Show #435 | India & World | Hindi & English | Kumar Gaurav Sir |
snippet.localized.description:
#Currentaffairs #KumarGauravSir #UtkarshClasses

01 Jan | Daily Current Affairs Live Show #435 | India & World | Hindi & English | Kumar Gaurav Sir |

प्रिय विद्यार्थियों,
प्रत्येक प्रतियोगी परीक्षाओं के लिए दैनिक समसामयिकी (करंट अफेयर्स) की महत्वपूर्ण भूमिका रहती है। इसी को ध्यान में रखकर आपकी तैयारी को और अधिक मजबूती प्रदान करने के लिए  प्रतिदिन प्रातः 6:00  बजे आपके प्यारे कुमार गौरव सर आप से रूबरू होते हैं और चर्चा करते हैं सुर्खियों में बने उन मुद्दों पर, जो कि परीक्षा के दृष्टिकोण को ध्यान में रखकर आपके लिए लेकर आते है। उनके इसी समर्पण भाव को आप सभी ने असीम स्नेह दिया और यह शो भारत का नंबर वन लाइव करंट अफेयर्स शो बन गया। इस नियमित लाइव क्लासेस में आप प्रमुख प्रतियोगी परीक्षाओं के लिए राष्ट्रीय एवं अंतर्राष्ट्रीय समसामयिकी जैसे- खेल, अंतर्राष्ट्रीय संबंध, विज्ञान व तकनीकी, राजव्यवस्था, पर्यावरण इत्यादि से जुड़ी कई जानकारियाँ प्राप्त करते हैं।

इस लाइव सेशन के बेहतरीन फीचर्स इस प्रकार है :
●दैनिक सुर्खियाँ ( #Daily_Current_Affairs )
●प्रेरक वाक्य या Motivational Quote  
●MCQ यानि बहुविकल्पात्मक प्रश्नों के माध्यम से करंट अफेयर्स की तैयारी
●10 सबसे महत्वपूर्ण प्रश्न 
●फूलपत्ती वाला सवाल 
● गुरुमंत्र
●Today's GS Questions
● विज्ञप्तियों से संबंधित जानकारियाँ इत्यादि।

तो जानिए बीते दिन के करंट अफेयर्स Kumar Gaurav Sir के साथ प्रतिदिन सुबह 6:00 बजे ।

snippet.title: Master Secrets & Trailer : Lokesh Kanagaraj breaks | Exclusive Interview | Vijay | Anirudh
snippet.description:
#Master 

Lokesh Kanagaraj Interview for Master.Master is an upcoming Indian Tamil-language action-thriller film written and directed by Lokesh Kanagaraj, and produced by Xavier Britto, under the banner XB Film Creators.The film stars Vijay and Vijay Sethupathi, with Malavika Mohanan, Arjun Das, Andrea Jeremiah and Shanthanu Bhagyaraj in supporting roles. The music for the film is composed by Anirudh Ravichander, while cinematography and editing are performed by Sathyan Sooryan and Philomin Raj.

snippet.title: New year 2021 muggulu by easy rangoli Suneetha || Amazing New year Kolam rangoli designs
snippet.description:
New year 2021 muggulu by easy rangoli Suneetha || Amazing New year Kolam rangoli designs.It is our tradition to draw kolam every day morning at the doorsteps.
There are many benefits of drawing kolam in front of the house.
It is auspicious and believes Goddess Lakshmi enters the house if kolam is drawn.
Kolam brings a lot of positive vibrations and energy to you and your home.
Draw kolam soon after you wake up and then do your prayers.
Kolam or rangoli ( रंगोली  ) is a part of Indian culture and transferred from generation to the next generation.
This ancient art form is also called as muggulu in parts of South India like Andhra Pradesh and Telangana.
People draw different creative rangoli kolam designs using kolam powder or muggu pindi which is 
actually crushed Lime stone powder available in different parts of India.
There are different types of rangoli or kolam designs like dots kolam, sikku kolam, padi kolam, Margazhi kolam.
People draw special rangoli designs for Festivals like Sankranthi (Pongal), Diwali (Deepavali), Vijaya Dashami (Dasara).
Women create deepam rangoli or kolam designs during Diwali festival time, create very big and Dhanurmasam muggulu (Margazhi) for Sankranthi or Pongal festival.
It is a belief among the people that drawing muggulu in front of the house in the early morning soon after wake brings
good fortune to them and their family.
People mix rice flour to limestone powder and prepare their own kolam powder. Muggulu can also be drawn with rice flour only.
These Beautiful and creative designs are decorated with flowers based on the occasion or festival.
#Newyear2021 #Newyear #Newyearkolam #Newyearmuggulu #Newyearrangoli

snippet.title: Remembering the Legend | Tribute to Kalabhavan Mani | Linto Kurian
snippet.description:
"REMEMBERING THE LEGEND"
A tribute to the legendary kalabhavan mani  ❤️

Kunnisseri Veettil Raman Mani (1 January 1971 – 6 March 2016), better known by his stage name Kalabhavan Mani, was an Indian film actor and singer. Mani started his career as a mimicry artist with the Kalabhavan troupe. He had starred in over 200 films, including Malayalam, Tamil, Kannada and Telugu films, and was renowned for his humorous characters and villain roles.

Mani won the National Film Award – Special Jury Award and Kerala State Film Award for his performance as Ramu in Vasanthiyum Lakshmiyum Pinne Njaanum (1999).

snippet.title: Phish "Dinner And A Rematch" Madison Square Garden — 12/31/95
snippet.description:
Exactly 25 years after the audience tied the band 1-1 in a chess rivalry, Phish challenges YOU to a rematch as part of a special New Year’s Eve “Dinner And A Movie”. We’ll be presenting Phish’s first New Year’s Eve show from Madison Square Garden — 12/31/95 — in its entirety, beginning at 8:30 pm ET.

We’ve teamed up with the fine folks at https://Chess.com to host the Band vs. Audience online chess game which will start right at the top of the show and move at a decent clip. In short, fans will have 5 minutes to move their piece (the band will have no more than that as well). At the end of 5 minutes, whichever move has the most votes is the ‘audience’ move. Stick around during the set breaks as the band joins in from their various homes, playing a few moves and providing scintillating commentary on the game. We will post and send out the actual game link on 12/31.

To pace yourself over a long evening, we present some chess cheese board recipes for extended grazing. Our friend Marissa Mullen put together two options — “Olive Cheese Dreams” and “Billy Bries” — with an easy ‘cheese by numbers’ guide. Feel free to swap out any of the ingredients if there’s something else you prefer. Pair with the bubbly of your choice. For dessert, chessboard cookies! Recipes can be found at https://livephi.sh/chessmenu

For this final webcast of the year, our beneficiary will be none other than The WaterWheel Foundation itself. Since 1997, the band and their fans have collaborated on a nationwide charitable endeavor by raising funds and donating the proceeds across the country. This year alone, collectively we have raised and donated nearly $750,000 to 27 different nonprofits during the Dinner And A Movie series. Join us in continuing to support those in need. Donate at https://www.phish.com/waterwheel

snippet.title: Welcome to BREATH - A 30 Day Yoga Journey  |  Yoga With Adriene
snippet.description:
It is happening! Today’s video is a bit of an orientation, a warm welcome, and an official kick-off. We will begin with a few easy group breaths to enjoy, and recognize that if all you do is arrive here to breathe, you are winning, golden, exactly where you are meant to be. 

You can consider this a practice day for your upcoming practices if you like. 

**IMPORTANT** If you are not signed up for the daily email that corresponds with each practice video, sign up for free and receive your free BREATH calendar here: https://www.yogawithadriene.com/breath

Work with what you have, but in this video, I make some suggestions on some optional things you might like to bring to class each day, along with an invitation to help guide you as you embark on this unique journey. 

Check-in with your willingness to be present, and remember for this to take off - you have to show up.

If this cross-legged position is not doable for you, you can use blankets, blocks, or pillows to sit up on. You can also come into a chair, or on the edge of your couch when we take this shape. That is a great way to modify and possibly a better spot for you to tune in, work with the breath technique, and warm up before we get moving into other shapes each day. 

Finally, set an intention. Be brave and ask WHY? Why are you here? What do you think pulled you here? And if you don’t know, that is okay, we will likely uncover that together. (How exciting!)

Let me know where you are practicing from in the comment section down below!

- - - - - - - - - - 

🧘🏽‍♂️🧘‍♀️Become a FWFG YOGA member! 🧘🏻‍♂️🧘🏿‍♀️
https://fwfg.com
Join Find What Feels Good and access over 700 videos including yoga and meditation for all levels. Explore daily practices, workshops, in depth learning, weekly or monthly accountability series, and an opportunity to connect with a one of a kind global community. This is your one stop shop for yoga, creativity, wellness, and all things FWFG. Try it FREE for 7 Days! 

- - - - - - - - - - 

❤️SUBSCRIBE to the YWA channel for free yoga videos every week and to support high-quality free yoga for all! ❤️
https://www.youtube.com/user/yogawithadriene?sub_confirmation=1

- - - - - - - - - - 

More at www.yogawithadriene.com
▶︎ Instagram: @adrienelouise
▶︎ Twitter: @yogawithadriene
▶︎ Facebook: Yoga With Adriene
▶︎ Shop: https://shop.fwfg.com

- - - - - - - - - -

If this cross-legged position is not doable for you, you can use blankets, blocks, or pillows to sit up on. You can also come into a chair, or on the edge of your couch when we take this shape. That is a great way to modify and possibly a better spot for you to tune in, work with the breath technique, and warm up before we get moving into other shapes each day. 

Finally, set an intention. Be brave and ask WHY? Why are you here? What do you think pulled you here? And if you don’t know, that is okay, we will likely uncover that together. (How exciting!)

Let me know where you are practicing from in the comment section down below!

snippet.title: I Troll BadBoyHalo with A Confusing Minecraft Mod
snippet.description:
Skeppy makes BadBoyHalo change his perspective. This was amazing.

Follow My Twitter - @Skeppy

Follow My Instagram - @Skeppy

Today I took BadBoyHalo on a tour of my home on the "new" Minecraft Server Update LMAO. BadBoyHalo gets lost and I have to save him (as usual), I show off my bedroom, mirror room and my farm and I think he got scared? He refuses to come to my house now? Bad absolutely lost his mind this video so if this gets 100,000 likes I might let him out of the simulation (or you could say: Bad absolutely lost his mind this video so if this does not get 100k likes may all your servers be CURSED)

Not Minecraft, But Water Rises or Minecraft, But Lava Rises, or any other but challenge like that. This is me pushing Bad to the edge of insanity.

Nessuno sa perché Pathfinder sia stato creato... ma una cosa è certa: non è fatto per servire ai tavoli. Sfida il pericolo in cerca di risposte insieme al tuo MRVN preferito. Ma scegli con attenzione le tue battaglie, perché in pochi ce la fanno.  
 
Apex Legends™ è un gioco gratuito in stile battle royale in cui personaggi leggendari si sfidano per gloria, fama e ricchezza ai margini della Frontiera. Gioca gratis su PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S e PC tramite Origin e Steam: http://x.ea.com/57366.

Przeznaczeniem Pathfindera na pewno nie jest obsługa stolików. Ruszaj na poszukiwania odpowiedzi ze swoim ulubionym Marvinem. Ostrożnie wybieraj walki – nie każdemu udaje się przetrwać 12 rund.  
 
Apex Legends™ to darmowa gra Battle Royale, w której legendarne postacie mierzą się ze sobą w walce o sławę i chwałę na obrzeżach Kresów. Na PlayStation® 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S oraz Origin i Steam na PC: http://x.ea.com/57366.

localizations.da.description:
Uanset hvad Pathfinder blev bygget til, var det ikke venlig betjening. Tag på en farefuld søgen efter svar med din foretrukne MRVN. Vælg dine kampe med omhu – ikke alle kan gå tolv omgange.  
 
Apex Legends™ er et gratis Battle Royale-spil, hvor legendariske figurer kæmper om hæder, berømmelse og held i grænseområdet. Spil gratis lige nu på PlayStation® 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S og pc via Origin og Steam: http://x.ea.com/57366.

localizations.es-MX.description:
Sea lo que sea por lo que se creó a Pathfinder, seguro que no fue para servir mesas. Embárcate en una peligrosa búsqueda por respuestas con tu MRVN favorito. Pero escoge tus peleas con cabeza, no todo el mundo logra hacer algo por mucho tiempo.  
 
Apex Legends™ es un juego gratuito estilo Battle Royale en el que personajes legendarios luchan por la gloria, la fama y la fortuna en los límites de la Frontera. Juega gratis ahora en PlayStation®4, PlayStation®5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S y PC a través de Origin y Steam: http://x.ea.com/57366.

localizations.nl-NL.description:
Waar Pathfinder ook voor is gebouwd, het is niet om tafels te bedienen. Begin aan een gevaarlijke zoektocht naar antwoorden met je favoriete MRVN. Maar kies je gevechten zorgvuldig: niet iedereen houdt het twaalf ronden vol.  
 
Apex Legends™ is een free-to-play battle royale-spel waarin legendarische personages strijden om glorie, roem en fortuin aan de rand van de Frontier. Speel nu gratis op de PlayStation®4, PlayStation®5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S en pc via Origin en Steam: http://x.ea.com/57366.

O Pathfinder pode ter sido construido para muita coisa. Mas não para servir à mesa. Vai em busca de respostas com o teu MRVN favorito. Mas escolhe bem as tua lutas. Nem todos duram 12 rounds.

localizations.ja.title: エーペックスレジェンズ | Stories from the Outlands – ファイトナイト
localizations.ja.description:
パスファインダーの製造目的は不明だが、少なくとも給仕用ではないことは確かだ。お気に入りのMRVNとともに答えを求めて危険な旅に出よう。だが、戦いに挑むには状況の見極めが肝心だ。12ラウンドを終えたとき、選ばれし者のみが勝者となる。
 
「エーペックスレジェンズ™」は、伝説の戦士が集結してフロンティアの辺境で富と栄誉と名声を懸けて戦う、基本プレイ無料のバトルロイヤル作品。PlayStation®4、PlayStation®5、Xbox One、Xbox Series X|S、Origin（PC）、Steam（PC）で今すぐ無料プレイ: http://x.ea.com/57366

localizations.zh-Hans.title: 《Apex Legends》| 外域故事 ──“激战之夜”
localizations.zh-Hans.description:
无论创造探路者的意义是什么，服务他人都绝对不在其中。与自己最爱的马文一起历经危险。寻找答案谨慎作战，不是每个人都能撑过十二回合。
 
《Apex Legends™》是一款免费大逃杀游戏，传奇角色们在边境边缘为荣誉、名望和财富而战。赶快在 PlayStation® 4、PlayStation 5、Xbox One、Xbox Series X|S 和 PC 端 Origin 以及 Steam 上免费游玩：http://x.ea.com/57366。

Apex Legends™ est un jeu de tir Battle Royale Free-to-Play où des personnages légendaires combattent ensemble aux confins de la Frontière pour la gloire et la fortune. Jouez gratuitement sur PlayStation®4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S et PC via Origin et Steam : http://x.ea.com/57366.

snippet.title: LAKERS at SPURS | FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | December 30, 2020
snippet.description:
LAKERS at SPURS | FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | December 30, 2020

LeBron James (26 PTS, 5 REB, 8 AST) led the Los Angeles Lakers to a 121-107 win over the San Antonio Spurs. With his 26 PTS, James has now scored 10+ PTS in 1,000-consecutive outings. Anthony Davis finished with 20 PTS and 8 REB, and Dennis Schroder supplied 21 PTS in the win. Dejounte Murray led the way for the Spurs with a career-high 29 PTS, 7 REB and 7 AST, and DeMar DeRozan provided 23 PTS and 6 AST for San Antonio.

Next Game:
Los Angeles Lakers at San Antonio Spurs – Jan. 1, 2021 at 8pm/et on NBATV

Subscribe to the NBA: https://on.nba.com/2JX5gSN 

Full Game Highlights Playlist: https://on.nba.com/2rjGMge

snippet.title: Film Theory: Titanic is about Time Travel... No REALLY!
snippet.description:
Subscribe to never miss a Film Theory! ► http://bit.ly/1dI8VBH    
Don't miss our Holliday Theory Wear!! ► https://bit.ly/2UkxCv0    

Titanic is a movie that has stood the test of time... and has one of the BIGGEST unanswered questions of any movie. No, I don't mean could they both fit on the door if Rose had just moved over a little. I mean the question is Jack a time traveler sent to make sure the Titanic sinks? Yes, that age old question. snippet.title: HORNETS at MAVERICKS | FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | December 30, 2020
snippet.description:
HORNETS at MAVERICKS | FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | December 30, 2020

The Charlotte Hornets defeated the Dallas Mavericks 118-99. The Charlotte bench led the way in the win as rookie LaMelo Ball finished with a team-high 22 PTS, 9 REB and 5 AST, and Miles Bridges added 20 PTS and 16 REB. Tim Hardaway Jr. led the scoring attack for the Mavericks with 18 PTS, and Luka Doncic finished with 12 PTS and 5 AST.

Next Games:
Memphis Grizzlies at Charlotte Hornets – Jan. 1, 2021 at 7pm/et on NBA League Pass
Miami Heat at Dallas Mavericks – Jan. 1, 2021 at 7pm/et on NBA League Pass

snippet.title: Welcome to BREATH - A 30 Day Yoga Journey  |  Yoga With Adriene
snippet.description:
It is happening! Today’s video is a bit of an orientation, a warm welcome, and an official kick-off. We will begin with a few easy group breaths to enjoy, and recognize that if all you do is arrive here to breathe, you are winning, golden, exactly where you are meant to be. 

You can consider this a practice day for your upcoming practices if you like. 

**IMPORTANT** If you are not signed up for the daily email that corresponds with each practice video, sign up for free and receive your free BREATH calendar here: https://www.yogawithadriene.com/breath

Work with what you have, but in this video, I make some suggestions on some optional things you might like to bring to class each day, along with an invitation to help guide you as you embark on this unique journey. 

Check-in with your willingness to be present, and remember for this to take off - you have to show up.

If this cross-legged position is not doable for you, you can use blankets, blocks, or pillows to sit up on. You can also come into a chair, or on the edge of your couch when we take this shape. That is a great way to modify and possibly a better spot for you to tune in, work with the breath technique, and warm up before we get moving into other shapes each day. 

Finally, set an intention. Be brave and ask WHY? Why are you here? What do you think pulled you here? And if you don’t know, that is okay, we will likely uncover that together. (How exciting!)

Let me know where you are practicing from in the comment section down below!

- - - - - - - - - -

https://fwfg.com
Join Find What Feels Good and access over 700 videos including yoga and meditation for all levels. Explore daily practices, workshops, in depth learning, weekly or monthly accountability series, and an opportunity to connect with a one of a kind global community. This is your one stop shop for yoga, creativity, wellness, and all things FWFG. Try it FREE for 7 Days! 

- - - - - - - - - - 

❤️SUBSCRIBE to the YWA channel for free yoga videos every week and to support high-quality free yoga for all! ❤️
https://www.youtube.com/user/yogawithadriene?sub_confirmation=1

- - - - - - - - - - 

More at www.yogawithadriene.com

snippet.title: New Year's 2021: Dubai puts on dazzling fireworks show from iconic Burj Khalifa
snippet.description:
The United Arab Emirates welcomed the new year in Dubai with a mesmerizing display of lights, fireworks and music from the world's tallest building, the iconic Burj Khalifa. 

The light show paid tribute to front-line health workers amid the coronavirus pandemic and displayed words of hope for 2021.

The UAE has imposed restrictions to slow the spread of COVID-19 on New Year’s Eve, including limiting social gatherings to 30 and under, and masks must be worn.

For more info, please go to https://globalnews.ca/news/7548867/new-years-eve-2020-coronavirus/

snippet.title: Defected Virtual Festival: We Dance As One 3.0 - #LiveStream
snippet.description:
The biggest HOUSE party in the world - this New Year's Eve. 🌎

December 31st, we will be bringing you this huge line-up to soundtrack your NYE house parties. Kicking off at 5pm UK time, we'll be running through until 1am.

We can't wait to see in 2021 with you and dance together, as one. 🕺💃

#HouseMusicAllLifeLong #WeDance #AsOne

snippet.title: WELCOME TO THE OTHER SIDE (NYE in virtual Notre Dame)
snippet.description:
Join & share the party on December 31st, 2020 at 23:25 (CET) & Paris-time!
Go to www.jeanmicheljarre.com to see how you can watch on Facebook, Twitter, VR, TV and Radio. 
WELCOME TO THE OTHER SIDE (The Album) is out now https://JMJ.lnk.to/WTTOSAW


**ENGLISH BELOW**

En partenariat avec la @Ville de Paris et sous le patronage de l'@UNESCO, le pionnier de la musique électronique @jeanmicheljarre s'associe à la start-up française VRrOOm pour nous emmener vers la nouvelle année avec un concert-spectacle innovant en  live-stream se déroulant depuis la célèbre cathédrale, Notre-Dame de Paris, en virtuelle et modélisée pour l’occasion. 

 «Welcome to the Other Side» est une expérience de concert gratuite unique, mondiale et ouverte à tous, dont l'ambition, au-delà de célébrer la nouvelle année de manière futuriste et festive, est d'envoyer un message d'espoir pour 2021 et pour la fin des temps sombres que nous traversons tous cette année: une invitation numérique et virtuelle de Paris, Ville Lumière, métropole animée des Arts et de la Culture,  abritant la cathédrale la plus célèbre au monde. Notre-Dame a une place unique dans l'imaginaire collectif, c'est un symbole de la force et du patrimoine mondial qui nous unit. 

Pour plus d’informations, rejoignez et suivez JMJ sur Facebook, Twitter, Instagram & YouTube, ou consultez :
www.jeanmicheljarre.com

Suivez Jean-Michel Jarre sur :
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/jeanmicheljarre/



Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/jeanmicheljarre
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/jeanmicheljarre/
YouTube: http://www.youtube.com/user/jeanmicheljarre?sub_confirmation=1

___________________________________________ 


In partnership with @Ville de Paris, and under the patronage of @UNESCO, Electronic Music pioneer @jeanmicheljarre teams up with French VR start-up VRrOOm to take us into the New Year with a Live-stream trailblazing concert-spectacular set in the virtual environment of the planetary landmark, Notre-Dame de Paris.

“Welcome to the Other Side” is a one-off exclusive, worldwide and open-to-all, free concert experience whose ambition, beyond celebrating the New Year in a futuristic and festive way, is to send a message of hope for 2021 and for the end of the dark times we are all going through this year: a digital and virtual invitation from Paris, the City of Light, vibrant metropole of the Arts & of Culture and home to the most famous cathedral in the world. Notre-Dame has a unique place in the collective imagination, it is a symbol of the strength and of World Heritage that binds us together.  
 
For all ongoing information follow JMJ on Facebook, Twitter, Instagram and YouTube or check: www.jeanmicheljarre.com
 
Follow Jean-Michel Jarre:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/jeanmicheljarre/ 
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/jeanmicheljarre 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/jeanmicheljarre/
YouTube: http://www.youtube.com/user/jeanmicheljarre?sub_confirmation=1

----
How to watch via Youtube, Facebook, Twitter, TV, radio or VR: for full details check www.jeanmicheljarre.com 

Here is how to join the VR experience: 

6DoF Concert:
- Download the VRChat app on Steam, Oculus or Viveport to watch the concert in virtual reality on all PC VR headsets, Oculus Quest and Quest 2 + link cable, or simply via PC
Once in VRChat, check the 'NOTRE-DAME CONCERT' icon in the WORLDS menu to access the concert. Attention, the world will be activated on December 31 at 11:23pm CET only (December 31 at 2:23pm PST).
Quest and Quest 2 users who are not equipped with the link cable will be able to access a lighter version of the concert!
REPLAYS WILL BE AVAILABLE TO ALL FOR 24 HOURS!

6DoF After-party:
- Download the VRChat app on Steam, Oculus or Viveport to watch the concert in virtual reality on all PC VR headsets, Oculus Quest and Quest 2 with or without link cable, or simply via PC
Once in VRChat, check the 'NOTRE-DAME AFTER-PARTY' icon in the WORLDS menu to access the party. Attention, the world will be activated starting January 1 at 00:13pm CET only (December 31 at 3:13pm PST).
Many suprises await you in the after-party world!
REPLAYS WILL BE AVAILABLE TO ALL FOR 4 DAYS UNTIL JANUARY 4!

3DoF Concert will be accessible inside Oculus Venues, from December 31 at 11:25pm to January 4.

#VR #NYE #NotreDame

snippet.title: New Year's Eve plea as UK COVID-19 cases reach record levels
snippet.description:
People have been told not to go out this New Year, after the UK recorded a record 55,892 coronavirus cases in the last 24 hours.

Public Health England's medical director Dr Yvonne Doyle made a passionate plea in response to the latest figures, urging everyone not to go out to celebrate New Year's Eve.

snippet.title: New Year's 2021: Sydney, Australia puts on stunning fireworks display
snippet.description:
Sydney, Australia put on a stunning fireworks show from Sydney Harbour Bridge and over the iconic Sydney Opera House to ring in 2021. In past years, 1 million people crowded the harbour to watch fireworks, but most watched on television this year as authorities urge residents to stay home due to the coronavirus pandemic.

Australia was among the first nations to usher in the New Year because of its proximity to the International Date Line, but is a grim end to the year for New South Wales and Victoria, the country’s two most populous states, which are battling to curb new COVID-19 outbreaks.

For more info, please go to https://globalnews.ca/news/7548867/new-years-eve-2020-coronavirus/

snippet.title: Noel Gallagher's High Flying Birds - We’re Gonna Get There In The End (Demo)
snippet.description:
"Firstly let me wish everyone a Happy New Year.
Things can only get better from here!! (saying that, they couldn’t get much worse could they?!)
Anyway I’ve been writing and noodling recently and I’ve made a little demo of a tune that I wrote a couple of weeks ago and it actually came out sounding pretty good … the lyrics are quite apt for the times and I think I’d like to share it with you.
The song is called ‘We’re Gonna Get There In The End’.
Hope your hangovers aren’t too horrific.
Hopefully we’ll catch up soon.
PS.  IT’S ONLY A DEMO.
ONWARDS.”
NG.

Lyrics:

Remember the dream that you’re keeping alive
Remember your love for the loved outside
Don’t fight the feeling
Don’t stop believing in what you know
‘Cause you can’t let go my friend
We’re gonna get there in the end 
 
Tonight! ... Tonight!
Gonna let that dream take flight
And when the morning comes
Will you wake up by my side?
 
Love – real - love
Is all I’m thinking of
Give it half a chance
The world might find a way
 
Don’t be afraid when you’re rolling the dice
Life is a trip that you don’t take twice
 
Don’t fight the feeling
Don’t stop believing in what you know
‘Coz you can’t let go my friend
We’re gonna get there in the end
 
Tonight!! ... Tonight!!
Gotta let that dream take flight
And when the morning comes
Will you wake up by my side?
 
Love – real - love
Is all I’m thinking of
Give it half a chance
The world might find a way
 
If you think that your faith is enough
The weight that you carry is love
We’ve spended too long inside
Let’s take a walk outside
It’s a sad, sad song that the world keeps singing
Well let love try to sing along

Don’t fight the feeling
Don’t stop believing in what you know
You can’t let go my friend
We’re gonna get there in the end

We’re gonna get there in the end
We’re gonna get there in the end 
 
--
JOIN NOEL GALLAGHER ONLINE:
Mailing List: https://NGHFB.lnk.to/signup 
Facebook: https://NGHFB.lnk.to/FB 
Twitter: https://NGHFB.lnk.to/TW 
Instagram: https://NGHFB.lnk.to/IG 

#NoelGallagher #NGHFB

snippet.description:
References:

Barnouw, Victor. 1977. Wisconsin Chippewa myths and tales and their relation to Chippewa life. Madison, WI: University of Wisconsin Press.

DeSanti, Brady. 2015. The Cannibal Talking Head: The Portrayal of the Windigo “Monster” in Popular Culture and Ojibwe Traditions. The Journal of Religion and Popular Culture. Volume 27, Issue 3 pp.186-201.

Rheault, D'arcy. 1999. Anishinaabe Mino-Bimaadiziwin - The Way of a Good Life: An Examination of Anishinaabe Philosophy, Ethics and Traditional Knowledge. Createspace Independent Pub.

Please do not re-upload the video. Please respect this decision. I'm trying to do the right thing.

snippet.title: Welcome to the new channel!
snippet.description:
Hello everyone- thank you for checking out my new YouTube Channel! I’m beyond excited to be starting my own shop and channel, and I hope you guys stick around as I get the whole video production situation sorted out! In the meantime the best place to follow along with the process of setting up the new shop is on Instagram (@will_stelter https://www.instagram.com/will_stelter/?hl=en) 

There’s tons of work to do to get the whole shop ready to make and produce knives and videos but I’m excited for the potential I see in it!

Go ahead and drop a comment of the sort of projects you’d like to see in the future!

Thanks,

-Will

snippet.title: LADY LESHURR - FAKE FLEX
snippet.description:
Directed by Spike Leesh. Shot & edited by Jay Goodz. Produced by Dusty Goodz. Back in October I got awarded a British Empire Medal from the Queen of England herself! So I hired out a mansion to celebrate. #ASTRONAUT EP IS OUT NOW!! https://music.apple.com/gb/album/astronaut-ep/1546512911
***LYRICS***

I woke up as a BEM winner
Queen of England sees me it’s like a looked in the mirror
I’m old school like a BBM pinger
And I make notes you can call me an EDM singer
I can’t stand these negative comments either they’re bitter
Talking like I fell off
TV shows just make the name bigger
I’m the queen of shade summer
And you’re the Queen of shadeborough
We ain’t built the same bruddah
And you don’t need to say nada
I can see it in your eyes that you’re vex enit
I just hired out a mansion just so I could flex in it
Fake ones I’ve detected it
These gyal disrespected it
Move up social distancing
Disinfected it
That’s my sis
If I do drill affi spit like this
That’s all you lot want these days
But I bet you’ll still say I make music for kids
Black men gotta do better than this 
That boy there ain’t innocent stop protecting him
Lost respect for him
He’s a brother but he’s not my next of kin
And he don’t even have to know me I’m a black woman and I’ve got to check a King
We got the equity
1 million contract rejected it
My bars hurt and they’re killing those victims
You’ve turned into a video vixen
Helped too many gyal sick of em switching
Making moves P Diddy I’m twitching
Oh my days what do we have here?
Them gyal there they cannot come near
Birmingham Queen that's who they all fear
They need a handout I’m like ere
Oh my days what do we have here?
Them gyal there they cannot come near
Birmingham Queen that's who they all fear
If they want bars then I got more for ya

snippet.title: !@#$%$#!! || Dubov vs Carlsen || Airthings Masters (2020)
snippet.description:
Follow me on Instagram for extra content https://www.instagram.com/agadmator/

Daniil Dubov vs Magnus Carlsen
Airthings Masters (2020), Round Quarterfinals, Game 3
Queen's pawn game (E10)

1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nf3 d5 4. g3 Bb4+ 5. Nbd2 dxc4 6. Bg2 a5 7. a3 Bxd2+ 8. Bxd2 b5 9. a4 c6 10. Qc2 Bb7 11. h4 Nbd7 12. h5 h6 13. Ne5 Nd5 14. Rh4 N7f6 15. Kf1 Qc7 16. Kg1 Nb4 17. Qc1 Rd8 18. axb5 cxb5 19. Bxb4 axb4 20. Ra7 Nd5 21. Rg4 Rg8 22. Qc2 c3 23. bxc3 bxc3 24. Ra3 Rc8 25. Nd3 Nf6 26. Bxb7 Qxb7 27. Nc5 Rxc5 28. dxc5 Nxg4 29. c6 Qxc6 30. Rxc3 Qb6 31. e3 Ke7 32. Rc6 Qd8 33. Qc5+ Kf6 34. Rd6 Qe7 35. Qd4+ Kg5 36. f3 f5 37. fxg4 Rc8 38. Qf4+ Kf6 39. Qxf5#

World Chess Champion Magnus Carlsen tops the field for the Airthings Masters, the 2nd stage of the Champions Chess Tour. The 12-player event will be played online on chess24 from December 26th to January 3rd and, as the first Major of the tour, features a $200,000 prize fund with $60,000 for 1st place. The winner also qualifies directly to the Grand Final in September 2021.

The tournament starts with a 3-day preliminary stage where the players play each other once before the top 8 go forward to a knockout. The time control is 15 minutes for all moves, with a 10-second increment from move 1. No draw offers are allowed before move 40. Official website: championschesstour.com

snippet.title: I Troll BadBoyHalo with A Confusing Minecraft Mod
snippet.description:
Skeppy makes BadBoyHalo change his perspective. This was amazing.

Follow My Twitter - @Skeppy

Follow My Instagram - @Skeppy

Today I took BadBoyHalo on a tour of my home on the "new" Minecraft Server Update LMAO. BadBoyHalo gets lost and I have to save him (as usual), I show off my bedroom, mirror room and my farm and I think he got scared? He refuses to come to my house now? Bad absolutely lost his mind this video so if this gets 100,000 likes I might let him out of the simulation (or you could say: Bad absolutely lost his mind this video so if this does not get 100k likes may all your servers be CURSED)

Not Minecraft, But Water Rises or Minecraft, But Lava Rises, or any other but challenge like that. This is me pushing Bad to the edge of insanity.

snippet.title: [avex官方HD] 王嘉爾 Jackson Wang & 林俊傑 JJ Lin - 過 Should've Let Go 官方完整版MV
snippet.description:
Jackson王嘉爾 × JJ林俊傑

雙J合璧，傾力創作全新單曲《過》(Should've Let Go)，
用音樂探討人生中，那些無法重來的選擇，
在MV敘事下，追回另一平行時空裡“如果有如果”的美好願望。
《過》(Should've Let Go)作為Jackson王嘉爾首次正式發行國語作品的開場。

12/18 《過》(Should've Let Go) MV 【avex全球同步發行】


Jackson王嘉爾和JJ林俊傑雙故事線單曲《過》MV正式上線，這次是來自Jackson王嘉爾和JJ林俊傑壹次創作力碰撞的“雙J合璧“。分別詮釋了兩條不同的遺憾故事線：想做卻未做的事，和遺憾做過的事，像兩個隔空談心的好朋友，通過音樂和妳交換遺憾的心事。

《過》MV用電影式的拍攝敘事手法，通過巴士作為鏈接，穿越時空演繹了兩條並行的故事線，結尾則閃現了另壹平行時空裏“如果有如果”的美好願望。



《過》(Should've Let Go)

演唱：王嘉爾 Jackson Wang / 林俊傑 JJ LIN 
作詞：林怡鳳 
作曲：林俊傑 JJ LIN/王嘉爾 Jackson Wang/BOYTOY  

回不去 的路口 oh oh
像過敏 紮了根 oh oh
我想起 某個人 oh oh
在我心中 被淡化的人 oh

我也有 某個人逗留 oh oh
是無法 根治的疼痛 oh oh
我以為 只能這樣了 oh oh
但回憶發作 思念難以負荷

愛情自帶寂寞  yeah
愛情各種錯過 oh oh
卻在多年以後
還想回頭

localizations.ja.title: 王嘉爾 Jackson Wang & 林俊傑 JJ LIN -《過》(Should've Let Go) Official Music Video
localizations.ja.description:
“過 とは、思い出を手放すこと。後悔と和解すること。”　
Jackson Wang王嘉爾ニューシングル《過》(Should've Let Go)。
JJ LIN林俊傑と組んで“2人のJ”が新たな音楽ストーリーを作り出す。
異なる音色が織りなすこの曲が“後悔と和解する”という気持ちを綿密に伝える。
平行する2つの物語が時空を超えて新たなストーリーにいる私たちを見返す。

Jackson Wang王嘉爾が時空を思い出す《過》(Should've Let Go)で初の中国語作品の第一幕を開く。
 
12/18 《過》(Should've Let Go)MV【avexより全世界配信開始】

 
“過 是對回憶放手 是和遺憾和解”
Jackson王嘉爾全新單曲《過》(Should've Let Go)，聯手JJ林俊傑“雙J合璧”碰撞出全新音樂故事，不同音色交織融合，多層次地傳遞“與遺憾和解”的情緒。MV雙故事線並行，穿越時空回看新故事下的我們。
Jackson王嘉爾選擇回憶時空《過》(Should've Let Go)作為首次正式發行國語作品的開場。
 
12/18 《過》(Should've Let Go)MV【avex全球同步發行】

localizations.zh-TW.title: [avex官方HD] 王嘉爾 Jackson Wang & 林俊傑 JJ Lin - 過 Should've Let Go 官方完整版MV
localizations.zh-TW.description:
Jackson王嘉爾 × JJ林俊傑

雙J合璧，傾力創作全新單曲《過》(Should've Let Go)，
用音樂探討人生中，那些無法重來的選擇，
在MV敘事下，追回另一平行時空裡“如果有如果”的美好願望。
《過》(Should've Let Go)作為Jackson王嘉爾首次正式發行國語作品的開場。

12/18 《過》(Should've Let Go) MV 【avex全球同步發行】


Jackson王嘉爾和JJ林俊傑雙故事線單曲《過》MV正式上線，這次是來自Jackson王嘉爾和JJ林俊傑壹次創作力碰撞的“雙J合璧“。分別詮釋了兩條不同的遺憾故事線：想做卻未做的事，和遺憾做過的事，像兩個隔空談心的好朋友，通過音樂和妳交換遺憾的心事。

《過》MV用電影式的拍攝敘事手法，通過巴士作為鏈接，穿越時空演繹了兩條並行的故事線，結尾則閃現了另壹平行時空裏“如果有如果”的美好願望。

snippet.description:

snippet.localized.description:

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | ARSENAL 1-4 MAN CITY | CARABAO CUP
snippet.description:
Holders Manchester City produced another Carabao Cup masterclass as we secured a comprehensive last-eight victory over Arsenal in North London to march into the semi-finals.

Second-half strikes from Riyad Mahrez, Phil Foden and Aymeric Laporte made it a night to remember after Gabriel Jesus’s third-minute opener had been cancelled out before the break.

The victory further extended manager Pep Guardiola’s incredible record in the League Cup and was no less than we deserved after what was another impressive all-round display.

snippet.title: A K -Drama Kiss - The BenZi Project
snippet.description:
#TheBENZIproject
Benjamin Kheng & Hirzi Zulkiflie
________________________________________________________________

A K-DRAMA KISS
Two long-lost lovers finally meet after years apart. Will they kiss, is there a twist, and how long is this theme song?

A K-Drama Kiss is supported by the National Arts Council as part of the #SGCultureAnywhere campaign. 

Co-produced by: Stardust Story

STARRING
Hirzi Zulkiflie
Benjamin Kheng

Directed & Written by Benjamin Kheng
Produced by: Hirzi Zulkiflie & Skye Chen
Line Producer: Catherine Therese Zhang Binbin
Director of Photography: Bong
1st Assistant Director:  Skye Chen
Production Manager: Sam Chua

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | CITY 2-0 NEWCASTLE | GUNDOGAN & TORRES
snippet.description:
City moved up to into the top five of the Premier League with an impressive 2-0 Boxing Day win over Newcastle United.

Gundogan and Torres on target as City see off Newcastle
Despite appalling conditions with rain and gale force winds lashing the Etihad, Pep Guardiola’s side went about their work in fine style.

Ilkay Gundogan struck early in the first half to give City a deserved lead – and Ferran Torres then added to our advantage with a second goal soon after the restart.

snippet.title: 百年难得一见的三岁小神童演迷你“老太太”唱「朝阳沟」 语出惊人 直接打动评委 和李伟健演夫妻逗乐大伙【我家有明星】
snippet.description:
#北京卫视 #我家有明星 是北京卫视文艺节目频道为孩子们搭建的一个舞台，开播以来深受京城儿童和父母的喜爱。这里是天才宝贝与稚嫩童心的表达乐园，汇集了最前沿的教育思维理念，萌宝们参加各种脑力与体力交织的奇趣挑战活动。该节目寓教于乐，旨在培养智商爆表和拥有惊人才艺的宝贝们。孩子不一定都要成为明星，但在成长道路上需要不断给自己加油！

snippet.title: Watch New Zealand's 2021 New Year fireworks display
snippet.description:
Kick-off New Year's Eve with Auckland, New Zealand, as the first major city to celebrate 2021.

It is expected we will see a vast laser display followed by an impressive show of fireworks. 

Auckland will be one of the few cities able to bid farewell to 2020 in style, as several cities including London and Las Vegas have cancelled their December 31 displays to prevent large crowds from gathering during the Covid-19 pandemic. 

Australia, who celebrate New Year's Eve just a few hours after New Zealand, will also allow events but under strict restrictions. 

Subscribe to The Telegraph on YouTube ► https://bit.ly/3idrdLH

Get the latest headlines: https://www.telegraph.co.uk/

Telegraph.co.uk and YouTube.com/TelegraphTV are websites of The Telegraph, the UK's best-selling quality daily newspaper providing news and analysis on UK and world events, business, sport, lifestyle and culture.

Kick-off New Year's Eve with Auckland, New Zealand, as the first major city to celebrate 2021.

It is expected we will see a vast laser display followed by an impressive show of fireworks. 

Auckland will be one of the few cities able to bid farewell to 2020 in style, as several cities including London and Las Vegas have cancelled their December 31 displays to prevent large crowds from gathering during the Covid-19 pandemic. 

Australia, who celebrate New Year's Eve just a few hours after New Zealand, will also allow events but under strict restrictions. 

Subscribe to The Telegraph on YouTube ► https://bit.ly/3idrdLH

Get the latest headlines: https://www.telegraph.co.uk/

Telegraph.co.uk and YouTube.com/TelegraphTV are websites of The Telegraph, the UK's best-selling quality daily newspaper providing news and analysis on UK and world events, business, sport, lifestyle and culture.

snippet.description:

snippet.title: Glitterbomb 3.0 vs. Porch Pirates
snippet.description:
Merry Christmas ya filthy animals.  If you want to learn the design fundamentals it takes to make something like the Glitter Bomb, enroll in my NEW Creative Engineering course at https://Monthly.com/MarkRober and I'll see you in class!

MY NEW MERCH!!!  https://markrober.store/

Thanks to SimpliSafe for providing the cameras.  Check out their biggest sale of the year by visiting http://simplisafe.com/markrober

Subscribe to Jim's channel here- https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBNG0osIBAprVcZZ3ic84vw

Biodegradable glitter courtesy of  https://www.altnaturals.com/pages/glitter

So stoked to finally announce my creative engineering class has just launched today! Enrollment is now open until Dec 27 at Monthly.com/MarkRober (link also in bio).

This class is a hands-on, 30-day learning experience that will teach you how to use engineering and science to bring your creative ideas to life.

During this class, I'm going to share with you my entire creative engineering process from start to finish. You're going to follow along with me as I fully design and engineer 3 brand new builds from scratch... from how I come up the idea, all the way through bringing the final builds to life.

The best part is, over the month, you'll follow along with me and my process, side by side, and you will leave the class with 3 original, creative builds of your own.

This is the class I wish I had when I was starting out. It's designed to take your skills to make cool stuff to the next level, whether you're a beginner or a more experienced maker/engineer.

The class officially starts on January 4, 2021, and it will only run a few times per year, so claim your spot if you're interested!

See you in class!

-Mark

snippet.title: The Illusion Only Some Can See
snippet.description:
Ames window illusion illustrates how we don't directly perceive external reality. Special Holiday deal! Go to https://NordVPN.com/veritasium and use code VERITASIUM to get 68% off a 2 year plan plus 4 additional months free. It’s risk free with Nord’s 30 day money-back guarantee!

snippet.title: Watch Australia's 2021 Sydney Harbour New Year fireworks celebrations
snippet.description:
Watch a 'toned down' firework display in Sydney Harbour this year, as Australia allows New Year's Eve events to happen, but under strict rules and restrictions. 

Anyone who wished to enter the Sydney Harbour 'Green Zone' on New Year's Eve needed to apply for an entry pass, with prime firework vantage points being designated for frontline workers.

People have been encouraged to limit non-essential gatherings over the New Year period where possible to further minimise the risk of transmission in the community.

Subscribe to The Telegraph on YouTube ► https://bit.ly/3idrdLH

MAHALAGANG PAALALA:

Muli po naming pinapaalala na hanggang ngayon ay SARADO PA RIN PO ANG AMING ACTION CENTER sa TV5 Media Center, Reliance Street, Mandaluyong City.

Hindi pa rin po maaaring pumunta nang personal ang mga complainant para magreklamo kay Idol Raffy dahil sa ating kinahaharap na pandemya at mahigpit pa ring ipinapatupad ang mga safety measures upang maging ligtas ang lahat.

Maraming salamat sa inyong pag-unawa at mag-ingat po tayong lahat!

snippet.title: The Beatles:  Get Back - A Sneak Peek from Peter Jackson
snippet.description:
PETER JACKSON REVEALS SNEAK PEEK OF HIS UPCOMING MUSIC DOCUMENTARY
“THE BEATLES: GET BACK” ONLINE AND STREAMING ON DISNEY+ 

Feature-Length Film Opens in Theatres August 27, 2021

Acclaimed filmmaker Peter Jackson has released an exclusive sneak peek of his upcoming documentary “The Beatles: Get Back” for fans everywhere to enjoy. The 5-minute special look is available to fans worldwide on TheBeatles.com and streaming on Disney+.
 
Jackson said, “We wanted to give the fans of The Beatles all over the world a holiday treat, so we put together this five-minute sneak peek at our upcoming theatrical film ‘The Beatles: Get Back.’ We hope it will bring a smile to everyone’s faces and some much-needed joy at this difficult time.”

Acclaimed filmmaker Peter Jackson’s “The Beatles: Get Back” is a unique cinematic experience that takes audiences back in time to The Beatles’ intimate recording sessions during a pivotal moment in music history... 

Read more at https://www.thebeatles.com/news/beatles-get-back-sneak-peek-peter-jackson

#TheBeatlesGetBack

Photo by Linda McCartney / © Paul McCartney

snippet.title: Neymar responde Sikêra Jr. sobre festa na casa do craque
snippet.description: O apresentador Sikêra Jr.abriu o Alerta Nacional desta quinta-feira (31) mostrado a mensagem que recebeu do jogador Neymar Jr. No dia anterior, Sikêra havia dito no programa que, se caso o craque lhe convidasse para sua suposta festa de Réveillon, ele iria, sem problema algum, com o elenco. O jogador do Paris Saint Germain respondeu dizendo que não fará festa, mas que logo após a pandemia sua casa estará de portas abertas para Sikêra Jr.

snippet.title: David Guetta | United at Home - Paris Edition from the Louvre
snippet.description:
DONATE NOW on https://davidguetta.com/donate

In partnership with @PlayStation France & @Xiaomi France 

After raising $1.5 million (USD) for charities and amassing over 50 million views in Miami and New York, “United At Home” continues from the iconic city of Paris with a phenomenal production in front of the Louvre museum’ glass pyramid. In an effort to unite people around the globe, David Guetta is inviting everyone to join him in celebrating NYE and spreading the holidays spirit to benefit UNICEF, Les Restos du Coeur and the Musée du Louvre.

snippet.title: Nosso hino - Japinha conde (clipe oficial)
snippet.description:
Nosso hino 

Bebi pra aliviar chorei pra descarregar compartilhei meus sofrimentos fiz amigos com o mesmo sentimentos, dividimos história sofridas o ombro de um amigo virou ponte recaída, não sei se foi acaso ou destino mais foi no Buteco que fizemos nosso hino 

Refrão:
E eu sou cachaceiro mesmo eu bebo mesmo, aí de quem falar de mim, eu bebo no litrão eu bebo no golinho esse é o hino dos cachaceiros do Brasil


Lílian Nunes
Mirian Salomão
Dan Poeta
Léo Mantovani
Gene Silvestre

snippet.description:
- SE TORNE UM MEMBRO DA SÉTIMA LEGIÃO! -
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCe6pKugTDyOPT1Md2DTybbQ/join

- Ouça o 7 Minutoz nas plataformas digitais -
Spotify: https://spoti.fi/2PFfw5M
Deezer: https://bit.ly/34uYsn9
Apple Music: https://apple.co/36vHkzN

VOZ por Pablo Matheuz (@pablomatheuzoficial)
COMPOSIÇÃO e LETRA por Lucas A.R.T. (@ucasberto) e Pablo Matheuz
BEAT por 808 Ander (@808_ander)
MIX/MASTER por Peu028 (@peu028)
EDIÇÃO por MB (@guzz_mb)

- LETRA -
[Intro]
Quem é o shinobi que afoga os traidores na batalha?
Cabelo cinza, caminhando sob as águas
Prodígio do Clã Senju
Não tenho medo de Bijuu
Olha o meu jutsu azul
Respeita o criador da Anbu

[Verso]
Eu sou frio e calculista
Tô dois passos a frente, cê não me engana
Quem é o mais brabo da vila?
Eles sabem que é o Tobirama
Não sabem metade do que eu sei
Olha o tanto de jutsu que eu criei
Kage Bunshin, Hiraishin e Edo Tensei
Manda avisar que eu sou a lei
Mano, olha pro meu Estilo Água
Me chamam de gênio, nasci com o dom
Se entrar no meu caminho é vala
Não tenho piedade, vai se afogar no Suiton
Eu e o meu irmão somos crianças que nasceram no meio da guerra
Vimos tanta morte, quase acostumamos com ela
Pra isso acabar de uma vez por todas
Nasce a Vila da Folha (tudo por Konoha!)
Eu não confio em quem é Uchiha
Conheço bem a maldição dessa família
O ódio, cedo ou tarde, os corromperia
E eu não posso arriscar a minha vila
Escute Madara Uchiha, você nunca será Hokage
Só sob o meu cadáver
Dominando os cinco elementos
Um shinobi a frente do tempo

[Ponte]
Esculpiram meu rosto nessa montanha
Minha força é tamanha, nenhum ninja me ganha
Mesmo que o primeiro tenha sido o Hashirama
Konoha sabe quem manda
Quem é o shinobi que afoga os traidores na batalha?
Cabelo cinza, caminhando sob as águas
Prodígio do Clã Senju
Não tenho medo de Bijuu
Olha o meu jutsu azul
Respeita o criador da Anbu

[REFRÃO]
Nidaime
O ninja criador de jutsus
Segundo Hokage
Suiton mais forte do mundo
Olha o tanto de água que eu tô invocando
Vou transformar sua vila num oceano
Nidaime
O ninja criador de jutsus
Segundo Hokage
Suiton mais forte do mundo
Fiquem avisados, eu não vou falar de novo
Uchiha bom é Uchiha morto

7 Minutoz © 2020 (@7mzoficial) #DropGameOver

snippet.title: ESPECIAL DE ANO NOVO TÉTE A THEO #MINHAPLAYBOI com Reynaldo Gianecchini e Marília Gabriela
snippet.description:
A tão esperada continuação do Especial de Natal #minhaplayboi com Reynaldo Gianecchini e Marilia Gabriela.
Entenda o por quê dos boatos, maldosos muitas vezes, envolvendo os três. Até fofoca de vício em heroína e carreira de modelo internacional do Theo tem!
Num especial de ano novo de redenção descobrimos quais as “sombras” de cada um. Uma intensa conversa sobre a inveja, luxúria, preconceito e rancor!
A sexualidade sendo o tema de uma forma evoluída e sem amarras.  
Saiba porque a Gabi gosta de borrar o batom é porque o Giane sempre foi o maduro da relação! 😂

Convidado ✨: https://instagram.com/reynaldogianecchini?igshid=etphujyb0w8y

snippet.title: Neujahrsansprache 2021 von Bundeskanzlerin Angela Merkel
snippet.description:
In ihrer Neujahrsansprache dankt Kanzlerin Merkel den Deutschen für ihre Geduld, sich auf diesen historischen Kraftakt der Virus-Bekämpfung einzulassen. Die schwere Zeit für unser Land sei noch nicht vorbei. Mit den ersten Geimpften habe aber jetzt die Hoffnung Gesichter. 

Viele seien über sich hinausgewachsen, ohne dies an die große Glocke zu hängen, so Merkel - etwa  Ärzt*innen und Pflegekräfte, Mitarbeiter der Gesundheitsämter und die Bundeswehr. Unzählige hätten zudem dazu beigetragen, dass das Leben trotz Pandemie weiter möglich sei.

Merkel wandte sich scharf gegen Versuche, die Gesundheitsgefahr generell in Zweifel zu ziehen. Die Kanzlerin betonte, am Ende eines "atemlosen Jahres" gelte es auch, innezuhalten und zu trauern. Viele hätten einen geliebten Menschen verloren. Sie könne nur ahnen, wie bitter es sich für diese Menschen anfühlen müsse, wenn von einigen Unverbesserlichen das Virus bestritten und geleugnet werde.

----- 

Hier auf ZDFheute Nachrichten erfahrt ihr, was auf der Welt passiert und was uns alle etwas angeht: Wir sorgen für Durchblick in der Nachrichtenwelt, erklären die Hintergründe und gehen auf gesellschaftliche Debatten ein. Diskutiert in Livestreams mit uns und bildet euch eure eigene Meinung mit den Fakten, die wir euch präsentieren.

Abonniert unseren Kanal, um nichts mehr zu verpassen.

Immer auf dem aktuellen Stand seid ihr auf http://www.ZDFheute.de/.

#Merkel #Neujahrsansprache #ZDFheute

snippet.title: WELCOME TO THE OTHER SIDE (NYE in virtual Notre Dame)
snippet.description:
Join & share the party on December 31st, 2020 at 23:25 (CET) & Paris-time!
Go to www.jeanmicheljarre.com to see how you can watch on Facebook, Twitter, VR, TV and Radio. 
WELCOME TO THE OTHER SIDE (The Album) is out now https://JMJ.lnk.to/WTTOSAW


**ENGLISH BELOW**

En partenariat avec la @Ville de Paris et sous le patronage de l'@UNESCO, le pionnier de la musique électronique @jeanmicheljarre s'associe à la start-up française VRrOOm pour nous emmener vers la nouvelle année avec un concert-spectacle innovant en  live-stream se déroulant depuis la célèbre cathédrale, Notre-Dame de Paris, en virtuelle et modélisée pour l’occasion. 

 «Welcome to the Other Side» est une expérience de concert gratuite unique, mondiale et ouverte à tous, dont l'ambition, au-delà de célébrer la nouvelle année de manière futuriste et festive, est d'envoyer un message d'espoir pour 2021 et pour la fin des temps sombres que nous traversons tous cette année: une invitation numérique et virtuelle de Paris, Ville Lumière, métropole animée des Arts et de la Culture,  abritant la cathédrale la plus célèbre au monde. Notre-Dame a une place unique dans l'imaginaire collectif, c'est un symbole de la force et du patrimoine mondial qui nous unit. 

Pour plus d’informations, rejoignez et suivez JMJ sur Facebook, Twitter, Instagram & YouTube, ou consultez :
www.jeanmicheljarre.com

Suivez Jean-Michel Jarre sur :
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/jeanmicheljarre/



Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/jeanmicheljarre
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/jeanmicheljarre/
YouTube: http://www.youtube.com/user/jeanmicheljarre?sub_confirmation=1

___________________________________________ 


In partnership with @Ville de Paris, and under the patronage of @UNESCO, Electronic Music pioneer @jeanmicheljarre teams up with French VR start-up VRrOOm to take us into the New Year with a Live-stream trailblazing concert-spectacular set in the virtual environment of the planetary landmark, Notre-Dame de Paris.

“Welcome to the Other Side” is a one-off exclusive, worldwide and open-to-all, free concert experience whose ambition, beyond celebrating the New Year in a futuristic and festive way, is to send a message of hope for 2021 and for the end of the dark times we are all going through this year: a digital and virtual invitation from Paris, the City of Light, vibrant metropole of the Arts & of Culture and home to the most famous cathedral in the world. Notre-Dame has a unique place in the collective imagination, it is a symbol of the strength and of World Heritage that binds us together.  
 
For all ongoing information follow JMJ on Facebook, Twitter, Instagram and YouTube or check: www.jeanmicheljarre.com
 
Follow Jean-Michel Jarre:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/jeanmicheljarre/ 
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/jeanmicheljarre 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/jeanmicheljarre/
YouTube: http://www.youtube.com/user/jeanmicheljarre?sub_confirmation=1

----
How to watch via Youtube, Facebook, Twitter, TV, radio or VR: for full details check www.jeanmicheljarre.com 

Here is how to join the VR experience: 

6DoF Concert:
- Download the VRChat app on Steam, Oculus or Viveport to watch the concert in virtual reality on all PC VR headsets, Oculus Quest and Quest 2 + link cable, or simply via PC
Once in VRChat, check the 'NOTRE-DAME CONCERT' icon in the WORLDS menu to access the concert. Attention, the world will be activated on December 31 at 11:23pm CET only (December 31 at 2:23pm PST).
Quest and Quest 2 users who are not equipped with the link cable will be able to access a lighter version of the concert!
REPLAYS WILL BE AVAILABLE TO ALL FOR 24 HOURS!

6DoF After-party:
- Download the VRChat app on Steam, Oculus or Viveport to watch the concert in virtual reality on all PC VR headsets, Oculus Quest and Quest 2 with or without link cable, or simply via PC
Once in VRChat, check the 'NOTRE-DAME AFTER-PARTY' icon in the WORLDS menu to access the party. Attention, the world will be activated starting January 1 at 00:13pm CET only (December 31 at 3:13pm PST).
Many suprises await you in the after-party world!
REPLAYS WILL BE AVAILABLE TO ALL FOR 4 DAYS UNTIL JANUARY 4!

3DoF Concert will be accessible inside Oculus Venues, from December 31 at 11:25pm to January 4.

#VR #NYE #NotreDame

In partnership with @PlayStation France & @Xiaomi France 

After raising $1.5 million (USD) for charities and amassing over 50 million views in Miami and New York, “United At Home” continues from the iconic city of Paris with a phenomenal production in front of the Louvre museum’ glass pyramid. snippet.title: Zerstöre 2020 - Die Challenge II Das schaffst du nie!
snippet.description:
Ciao 2020, es war  schönwar schön mit dir - NICHT! Deshalb lassen wir es bei „Das schaffst du nie!“ zum Jahresende so richtig knallen und zerstören das Jahr 2020! Genauer gesagt: Sebastian Meinberg aka der Zerstörer übernimmt das höchstpersönlich. In dieser DSDN-Challenge soll Meini, stellvertretend für die ganze Welt und im persönlichen Auftrag von Marc Seibold, das Jahr 2020 so richtig kaputt machen. 2020 soll brennen, auseinander fallenauseinanderfallen, durchbrochen und zerschossen werden! FCK 2020!
 
MEINI VS. 2020 

Auf Sebastian Meinberg lastet wohl der bisher größte Druck seines Lebens: Bei der „Das schaffst du nie!“-Silvester-Challenge muss er 2020 zerstören. Wenn Meini das nicht schafft, wird 2021 genauso weitergehen. Das wäre wohl wirklich das Worst Case Szenario! Und eine Strafe für uns alle! Deshalb: Go Meini, Go Meini! Doch wie zu erwarten, bringt die DSDN-Zerstör-Challenge von Marc Seibold natürlich auch Schwierigkeiten mit sich. Schließlich hat sich das Jahr 2020 schon so in unsere Köpfe, Herzen und Leben eingebrannt, dass sich das nicht mal eben so kaputt machen lässt!  Meini wird aber alles geben, um dem Jahr 2020 an seinem letzten Tag zu zeigen, was es uns alles angetan hat! 

SO WAR DAS DSDN-JAHR 2020 

Mit einer fulminanten Zerstör-Challenge verabschieden wir uns vom Jahr 2020! Was haben wir dieses Jahr nicht alles erlebt bei „Das schaffst du nie!“. Wir starteten mit der 24 Stunden Insel-Challenge und der darauffolgenden, heiß ersehnten Achterbahnstrafe für Marc ins Jahr. Wir führten unsere neue Reihe „DSDN Classics“ ein, Ari telefonierte ganz 24 Stunden mit euch, Marc musste endlich alle seine Sozialstrafen ableisten, wir machten drei knallharte Verstecken-Challenges, Meini musste 24 Stunden Autoscooter fahren und und und. Es ging hoch hinaus und wieder tief hinunter, es war eiskalt und wurde richtig heiß, es war schmerzhaft, peinlich und unfassbar lustig. Und das alles war wieder mal nur möglich dank eurer großartigen Unterstützung! Danke liebe DSDN-Community für euren Support, eure Kommentare und Likes, euer Lob und eure Kritik und die viele Liebe. Wir sehen uns 2021 - wenn hoffentlich alles besser wird. (habe beim Lesen eine kleine Träne wegdrücken müssen) 

Welches DSDN Video hat euch im Jahr 2020 am besten und welches am wenigsten gefallen? Schreibt es uns in die Kommentare!  

 

#DSDN #Dasschaffstdunie #funk #Challenge 

******************************************************************** 

Ob 72 Stunden moderieren, eine Skischanze hochrennen oder eine Skulptur aus Eis schnitzen: Bei „Das schaffst du nie!“ stellt der fiese Redakteur Marc Seibold den zwei Hosts Ariane Alter und Sebastian Meinberg immer abwechselnd eine Challenge – gerne auch 24 Stunden lang. Schaffen die Hosts die Challenge, dürfen sie Marc bestrafen. Schaffen sie es nicht, müssen sie noch eine Bestrafung ertragen. Jeden Donnerstag um 15 Uhr gibt’s ein neues Video von „Das schaffst du nie!“. Heute: Die Zerstör-Challenge! Auf jede neue Challenge kommt am darauffolgenden Donnerstag die Bestrafung.  

Wer Sebastian bei der nächsten Challenge sehen möchte, klickt hier: https://www.instagram.com/heinz.wescher/ 

Und wer Marc folgen möchte, klickt hier: https://instagram.com/marc_cyborg ▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬ 

Yo! Wir gehören auch zu #funk! Checkt da mal vorbei: 

YouTube: https://youtube.com/funkofficial 

funk Web-App: https://www.funk.net/ 

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/funk/ 

Impressum: http://go.funk.net/impressum

Wir sehen uns 2021 - wenn hoffentlich alles besser wird. (habe beim Lesen eine kleine Träne wegdrücken müssen) 

Welches DSDN Video hat euch im Jahr 2020 am besten und welches am wenigsten gefallen? Schreibt es uns in die Kommentare!  

 

#DSDN #Dasschaffstdunie #funk #Challenge 

******************************************************************** 

Ob 72 Stunden moderieren, eine Skischanze hochrennen oder eine Skulptur aus Eis schnitzen: Bei „Das schaffst du nie!“ stellt der fiese Redakteur Marc Seibold den zwei Hosts Ariane Alter und Sebastian Meinberg immer abwechselnd eine Challenge – gerne auch 24 Stunden lang. Schaffen die Hosts die Challenge, dürfen sie Marc bestrafen. Schaffen sie es nicht, müssen sie noch eine Bestrafung ertragen. Jeden Donnerstag um 15 Uhr gibt’s ein neues Video von „Das schaffst du nie!“. Heute: Die Zerstör-Challenge! Auf jede neue Challenge kommt am darauffolgenden Donnerstag die Bestrafung.  

Wer Sebastian bei der nächsten Challenge sehen möchte, klickt hier: https://www.instagram.com/heinz.wescher/ 

Und wer Marc folgen möchte, klickt hier: https://instagram.com/marc_cyborg ▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬

snippet.title: Welcome to BREATH - A 30 Day Yoga Journey  |  Yoga With Adriene
snippet.description:
It is happening! Today’s video is a bit of an orientation, a warm welcome, and an official kick-off. We will begin with a few easy group breaths to enjoy, and recognize that if all you do is arrive here to breathe, you are winning, golden, exactly where you are meant to be. 

You can consider this a practice day for your upcoming practices if you like. 

**IMPORTANT** If you are not signed up for the daily email that corresponds with each practice video, sign up for free and receive your free BREATH calendar here: https://www.yogawithadriene.com/breath

Work with what you have, but in this video, I make some suggestions on some optional things you might like to bring to class each day, along with an invitation to help guide you as you embark on this unique journey. 

Check-in with your willingness to be present, and remember for this to take off - you have to show up.

If this cross-legged position is not doable for you, you can use blankets, blocks, or pillows to sit up on. You can also come into a chair, or on the edge of your couch when we take this shape. That is a great way to modify and possibly a better spot for you to tune in, work with the breath technique, and warm up before we get moving into other shapes each day. 

Finally, set an intention. Be brave and ask WHY? Why are you here? What do you think pulled you here? And if you don’t know, that is okay, we will likely uncover that together. (How exciting!)

Let me know where you are practicing from in the comment section down below!

snippet.title: Leider...
snippet.description:
Hallo Zusammen, 
leider muss ich euch mitteilen, das Bea am 12.12. nach langer schwerer Krankheit im  engen Kreis der Familie verstorben ist. 
Wie einige von euch ja mitbekommen haben, ging es Bea in den letzten Monaten zunehmend schlechter, mit vielen Höhen und Tiefen.

Die Zeit die uns noch blieb haben wir als Familie natürlich für uns genutzt und die letzten Wochen brauchte Ich und auch die Familie erst einmal emotionalen Abstand von Youtube. Die Meisten werden das verstehen können.

Es gibt einen schönen Brauch, den „Kerzentermin“ , wer mag und Zeit hat, zündet heute Abend gegen 20 Uhr eine Kerze für Bea an, dann sind es viele Menschen die gleichzeitig an Sie denken.

Wir haben auch besprochen wie es hier auf dem Kanal weitergehen wird. Dazu kommt zu späterer Zeit eine Info.

Mit traurigen Grüßen
Thomas

Musik: Emotional Love Theme - Biz Baz Studio

snippet.title: Watch Australia's 2021 Sydney Harbour New Year fireworks celebrations
snippet.description:
Watch a 'toned down' firework display in Sydney Harbour this year, as Australia allows New Year's Eve events to happen, but under strict rules and restrictions. 

Anyone who wished to enter the Sydney Harbour 'Green Zone' on New Year's Eve needed to apply for an entry pass, with prime firework vantage points being designated for frontline workers.

People have been encouraged to limit non-essential gatherings over the New Year period where possible to further minimise the risk of transmission in the community.

Subscribe to The Telegraph on YouTube ► https://bit.ly/3idrdLH

Get the latest headlines: https://www.telegraph.co.uk/

Telegraph.co.uk and YouTube.com/TelegraphTV are websites of The Telegraph, the UK's best-selling quality daily newspaper providing news and analysis on UK and world events, business, sport, lifestyle and culture.

snippet.title: Leben unter Polizeischutz | Reupload | doku
snippet.description:
+++Sendung wurde vor "Corona" produziert+++

Sein Leben ist massiv bedroht: Hamed Abdel-Samad lebt seit fünf Jahren unter Polizeischutz. Das heißt: 24 Stunden Rundumbewachung durch eine Spezialeinheit des Landeskriminalamtes Berlin. Kein fester Wohnsitz, Bewegung in gepanzerten Fahrzeugen, sogar im Flugzeug fliegen bewaffnete Beamte mit. Grund dafür ist ein internationaler Mordaufruf von Dschihadisten und Salafisten. Die Fatwa gegen den deutsch-ägyptischen Schriftsteller ist bis heute in Kraft.  Auslöser waren vor allem seine islamkritischen Thesen. RE zeigt den hohen Einsatz zum Schutz des Menschenrechts auf Meinungsfreiheit.

snippet.localized.title: Leben unter Polizeischutz | Reupload | doku
snippet.localized.description:
+++Sendung wurde vor "Corona" produziert+++

Sein Leben ist massiv bedroht: Hamed Abdel-Samad lebt seit fünf Jahren unter Polizeischutz. Das heißt: 24 Stunden Rundumbewachung durch eine Spezialeinheit des Landeskriminalamtes Berlin. Kein fester Wohnsitz, Bewegung in gepanzerten Fahrzeugen, sogar im Flugzeug fliegen bewaffnete Beamte mit. Grund dafür ist ein internationaler Mordaufruf von Dschihadisten und Salafisten. Die Fatwa gegen den deutsch-ägyptischen Schriftsteller ist bis heute in Kraft.  Auslöser waren vor allem seine islamkritischen Thesen. RE zeigt den hohen Einsatz zum Schutz des Menschenrechts auf Meinungsfreiheit.

snippet.title: WELCOME TO THE OTHER SIDE [Trailer] – join Jean-Michel Jarre on NYE in Virtual Reality NOTRE DAME
snippet.description:
In partnership with @Ville de Paris, and under the patronage of @UNESCO, Electronic Music pioneer @jeanmicheljarre teams up with French VR start-up VRrOOm to take us into the New Year with a live-stream trailblazing concert-spectacular set in the virtual environment of the planetary landmark, Notre-Dame de Paris.

Join & share the party on December 31st, 2020 at 23:25 (CET) & Paris-time: https://youtu.be/VKjFjFtKBRI

Go to www.jeanmicheljarre.com to see how you can watch on Facebook, Twitter, VR, TV and Radio. 

Here is how to join the VR experience: 
Concert:
- Download the VRChat app on Steam, Oculus or Viveport to watch the concert in virtual reality on all PC VR headsets, Oculus Quest and Quest 2 + link cable, or simply via PC
Once in VRChat, check the 'NOTRE-DAME CONCERT' icon in the WORLDS menu to access the concert. Attention, the world will be activated on December 31 at 11:23pm CET only (December 31 at 2:23pm PST).
Quest and Quest 2 users who are not equipped with the link cable will be able to access a lighter version of the concert!

After-party:
- Download the VRChat app on Steam, Oculus or Viveport to watch the concert in virtual reality on all PC VR headsets, Oculus Quest and Quest 2 with or without link cable, or simply via PC
Once in VRChat, check the 'NOTRE-DAME AFTER-PARTY' icon in the WORLDS menu to access the party. Attention, the world will be activated starting January 1 at 00:13pm CET only (December 31 at 3:13pm PST).
Many suprises await you in the after-party world!
 
For all ongoing information follow JMJ on Facebook, Twitter, Instagram and YouTube or check: www.jeanmicheljarre.com
 
Follow Jean-Michel Jarre:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/jeanmicheljarre/ 
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/jeanmicheljarre 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/jeanmicheljarre/
YouTube: http://www.youtube.com/user/jeanmicheljarre?sub_confirmation=1

Choose your music service to listen to Jean Michel Jarre: https://jean-michel-jarre.lnk.to/JMJ 

#VR #NYE #NotreDame

snippet.title: heute 19:00 Uhr vom 30.12.2020
snippet.description:
Das Robert-Koch-Institut meldet erstmals über 1.000 Todesfälle binnen 24 Stunden im Zusammenhang mit dem Coronavirus in Deutschland. Es gab außerdem 22.459 Neuinfektionen. Diese und weitere Nachrichten des Tages in den ZDFheute Nachrichten um 19 Uhr.

00:00 Vorspann
 
00:50 Corona: hohe Zahl an Toten
Mehr als 1.110 Corona-Tote werden gemeldet – darunter wohl aber auch Nachmeldungen. Gesundheitsminister Spahn rief im Hinblick auf Silvester dazu auf, die Beschränkungen einzuhalten.
 
03:22 Impfen von besonders Gefährdeten
Die Corona-Impfungen für besonders Gefährdete haben bereits begonnen – darunter fallen auch Menschen über 80 Jahre. Mobile Impfteams sind für Senioren- und Pflegeheime verantwortlich.
 
05:51 Brexit-Deal beschlossen
Der Brexit-Deal wird heute endlich abgeschlossen. Nach der EU-Spitze und dem britischen Unterhaus fehlt jetzt noch die Zustimmung des Oberhauses und der Queen.
 
08:48 „Riesiger politischer Erfolg“
Nach jahrelangen, zähen Verhandlungen ist der Ausstieg Großbritanniens aus der EU perfekt. ZDF-Korrespondentin Diana Zimmermann berichtet aus London.
 
10:08 EU und China: Einigung auf Abkommen
Nach fast siebenjährigen Verhandlungen steht nun ein Investitionsabkommen zwischen der Europäischen Union und China. Nach den USA ist China zweitgrößter Handelspartner der EU.
 
14:02 Zu warm und zu trocken
Alarmierende Nachrichten des Deutschen Wetterdienstes: 2020 war das zweitwärmste Jahr seit Beginn der Wetteraufzeichnung in Deutschland. Die Forderung: Mehr Klimaschutz.

-----

Hier auf ZDFheute Nachrichten erfahrt Ihr, was auf der Welt passiert und was uns alle etwas angeht: Wir sorgen für Durchblick in der Nachrichtenwelt, erklären die Hintergründe und gehen auf gesellschaftliche Debatten ein. Diskutiert in Livestreams mit uns und bildet Euch Eure eigene Meinung mit den Fakten, die wir Euch präsentieren. 

Abonniert unseren Kanal, um nichts mehr zu verpassen. 

Immer auf dem aktuellen Stand seid ihr auf https://www.heute.de/

#Shutdown #Verlängerung #ZDFheute

snippet.title: PTBS: So krass verändert ein Trauma Franzys Leben | reporter
snippet.description:
😱 Trauma, Flashback, Trigger – eine Posttraumatische Belastungsstörung (PTBS) haben nicht nur Soldat*innen! PTBS ist eine normale psychische Erkrankung, die viele Ursachen haben kann: Krieg, Folter, Unfälle, aber auch sexualisierte Gewalt und andere Gewalterfahrungen. Folgen und Symptome sind vielfältig: Schlafstörungen, Reizbarkeit, Konzentrationsschwäche. Aber auch das Risikio für eine Depression steigt. 
Franzy aus Augsburg ist 19 Jahre alt und will über den Ursprung ihrer PTBS nicht sprechen. Fest steht: Sie hat im Alltag durch die Erkrankung heftige Probleme. Aber auch eine große Hilfe: ihre Assistenzhündin Frieda. 🐶
 
🎶 Musik: 
Mr Roth, Noah Bentfield, R. Time - Drama Parlour
Mr Roth, Noah Bentfield, R. Time - Trapped in Reality
Cosimo Erario - An Unusual Tomorrow
Moritz Bintig - Strange Things Happen
Florian Thaller - Digital Era
 
💊 Die Assistenzhündin Frieda kann “anzeigen”, wenn sie merkt, dass Franzy einen Anfall bekommt. Wenn es schon zu spät ist, kann Frieda bellen, Medikamente und Hilfe holen. Franzy hat Frieda teilweise selbst ausgebildet, teilweise mithilfe eines professionellen Assistenzhundetrainers. 
 
🐕 Assistenzhunde dürfen in der Regel auch Orte betreten, wo Hunde sonst verboten sind, z.B. Supermärkte, Krankenhäuser oder Behörden. Grundlage hierfür sind die UN-Behindertenrechtskonvention (UN-BRK) und das Bundes-Behindertengleichstellungsgesetz (BGG).
Mehr Infos dazu gibt es hier: 
https://www.pfotenpiloten.org/gesetze/#zutritt 
 
👩‍⚕️ Fatima hat vor dem Dreh mit der PTBS-Expertin Ulrike Schultheis gesprochen. Sie ist Chefärztin der Abteilung für Psychosomatische Medizin und Psychotraumatologie der LVR-Klinik Köln – dort gibt es auch eine Traumaambulanz. 
 
😔 Frau Schultheiß geht davon aus, dass 2-5 Prozent der Gesellschaft eine PTBS haben. Es wird eine Dunkelziffer vermutet, daher gibt es keine genauen Zahlen. Man unterscheidet zwischen einer klassischen (ausgelöst durch ein bestimmtes Traumaereignis) und einer komplexen PTBS (augelöst durch Gewalt oder andere Traumaerlebnisse über einen längeren Zeitraum).
 
📊 Die Wahrscheinlichkeit eine PTBS zu bekommen ist Expert*innen zufolge bei Frauen höher als bei Männern – weil bei Frauen die Wahrscheinlichkeit höher sei, Gewalt zu erfahren. Schätzungen zufolge liegt die Wahrscheinlichkeit bei Frauen bei 10-12 Prozent und bei Männern bei 5-6 Prozent. Mehr dazu gibt es hier:
https://psychiatrie.charite.de/fuer_patienten/krankheitsbilder/posttraumatische_belastungsstoerungen_ptbs/
Und hier:
https://www.bundestag.de/resource/blob/490504/8acad12ffbf45476eecdfeff7d6bd3f4/wd-9-069-16-pdf-data.pdf 

🆘 Wo gibt’s Hilfe?
PTBS kann behandelt werden! Mit Psychotherapie und in einigen Fällen zusätzlich mit Medikamenten. Man kann zuerst zur Hausärztin gehen, oder direkt zu einem Therapeuten, in eine psychiatrische Klinik oder in eine Traumaambulanz. 
 
📞 Telefonseelsorge:
https://www.telefonseelsorge.de/
Tel: 08001110111 (kostenfrei)
 
👉 Übersicht der Traumaambulanzen in Deutschland:
https://www.bmjv.de/SharedDocs/Downloads/DE/Themen/OpferhilfeUndGewaltpr%C3%A4vention/Opferbeauftragter/Uebersicht_Traumaambulanzen.html 
 
 
🎞 Team: Fatima Talalini, Gregor Simbruner, Frédéric Sapart, Lea Brockmann, Andreas Josef, Julia von Cube
 
👉 Ihr findet uns auch hier:  
Twitter: https://twitter.com/reporter 
Facebook: http://facebook.com/reporter.offiziell/ 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/reporter.offiziell/ 
Snapchat: https://www.snapchat.com/discover/Reporter/3246991136 
 
👉 #reporter gehört zu #funk: 
YouTube: http://youtube.com/funkofficial 
funk Web-App: http://go.funk.net 
Facebook: http://facebook.com/funk
 
Erlebt mit uns echte Storys. Nah dran. Kritisch. Ohne Filter. 💙
Jede Woche ein neues Thema. 🎥
 
🖖 Hallo! Ich heiße Fatima. Ich habe schnell gemerkt: Ich lerne viel mehr über die Welt, wenn ich mit Menschen spreche, die ganz anders sind als ich! Ich will wissen, wie die Welt funktioniert und auf Ideen schauen, wie wir sie besser machen können. Na dann los, Käffchen? Instagram: @fatimautopie
 
👉 reporter wird vom Programmbereich Aktuelles des WDR für funk produziert. funk ist ein Gemeinschaftsangebot der Arbeitsgemeinschaft der Rundfunkanstalten der Bundesrepublik Deutschland (ARD) und des Zweiten Deutschen Fernsehens (ZDF). http://go.funk.net/impressum
